    <description>The principal purpose of this study is to compare the modular seleXys PC Cup with a vitamys inlay to the monoblock RM Pressfit vitamys cup by means of wear rate. In addition, the migration of the two cups and the optimys stem, respectively, will be evaluated.</description>
